00:23:59.340 --> 00:24:01.220
I remember our first meeting was

00:24:02.140 --> 00:24:03.220
at your fifth birthday party.

00:24:03.980 --> 00:24:05.260
You insisted on having

00:24:05.420 --> 00:24:06.820
the rose candy.

00:24:08.140 --> 00:24:09.380
Now, I'm giving it to you.

00:24:28.660 --> 00:24:30.220
To the 18-year-old Song Zhizhi,

00:24:30.940 --> 00:24:32.380
also the 18-year-old Anne,

00:24:33.020 --> 00:24:33.660
hello.

00:24:34.020 --> 00:24:35.340
This is the first design draft

00:24:35.460 --> 00:24:36.260
you published online.

00:24:37.340 --> 00:24:38.620
This was the starting point
of your career.

00:24:39.100 --> 00:24:40.420
I thought it was meaningful.

00:24:41.460 --> 00:24:42.700
So, I made it myself.

00:24:43.540 --> 00:24:44.100
For you.

