00:25:22.140 --> 00:25:22.980
every single pencil for you.

00:25:30.740 --> 00:25:31.420
Zhizhi,

00:25:32.980 --> 00:25:34.380
this gift is very precious

00:25:35.740 --> 00:25:36.500
to me.

00:25:39.700 --> 00:25:40.860
It's the design manuscript

00:25:42.380 --> 00:25:44.100
that my mom never published
before she passed away.

00:25:46.140 --> 00:25:47.580
She was always studying

00:25:48.020 --> 00:25:49.780
how to incorporate
ancient gold craftsmanship into designs.

00:25:51.260 --> 00:25:52.500
I'm giving it to you now.

00:25:53.900 --> 00:25:55.460
Hope it inspires you.

00:25:57.140 --> 00:25:58.220
I will support your career

00:25:59.020 --> 00:26:00.100
every step of the way.

00:26:15.460 --> 00:26:15.900
Zhizhi.

00:26:19.420 --> 00:26:20.460
I never imagined

00:26:22.460 --> 00:26:23.260
you would

00:26:23.300 --> 00:26:24.620
come into my life like this.

00:26:25.500 --> 00:26:26.860
You threw all my plans and arrangements

00:26:28.260 --> 00:26:29.140
into disarray,

00:26:32.380 --> 00:26:33.780
turning my world upside down.

00:26:37.260 --> 00:26:38.420
We've taken such a winding path,

00:26:40.700 --> 00:26:41.620
and I've made you wait far too long.

00:26:42.980 --> 00:26:43.500
I'm sorry.

00:26:50.660 --> 00:26:51.900
It's all my fault for being so hesitant,

00:26:53.420 --> 00:26:55.300
for not telling you
how I felt about you sooner.

00:26:59.540 --> 00:27:00.060
For the rest of my life,

00:27:01.500 --> 00:27:03.140
I want to do my utmost

00:27:04.740 --> 00:27:06.460
to take care of and protect you.

00:27:10.980 --> 00:27:11.700
I want to marry you.

00:27:11.700 --> 00:27:12.530
♪Never thought I'd need someone♪

00:27:12.900 --> 00:27:14.380
♪When I cry♪

00:27:17.430 --> 00:27:21.980
♪Then you came along.
You bring the light♪

00:27:25.300 --> 00:27:26.060
Zhizhi.

00:27:28.660 --> 00:27:29.700
Marry me.

00:27:32.580 --> 00:27:33.300
Will you?

00:27:39.100 --> 00:27:39.820
I will.

00:27:39.820 --> 00:27:42.580
♪You're always there,
and you are everywhere♪

00:27:45.650 --> 00:27:47.980
♪You take me to the sky♪

00:27:48.580 --> 00:27:51.180
♪And you take away the pain♪

00:27:51.940 --> 00:27:58.180
♪'Cause I see sparks fly
whenever you smile♪

