♪To me♪

00:29:03.780 --> 00:29:04.380
Mr. Song,

00:29:05.100 --> 00:29:06.340
as Zhizhi mentioned last time,

00:29:06.780 --> 00:29:08.340
we could establish a new joint venture

00:29:08.900 --> 00:29:09.820
and move the Quefeng project

00:29:09.860 --> 00:29:11.060
to this new company,

00:29:11.620 --> 00:29:13.180
where Jihong Group will

00:29:13.220 --> 00:29:14.060
inject capital.

00:29:14.540 --> 00:29:15.780
This will provide
sufficient financial support

00:29:16.140 --> 00:29:17.580
to address Starlight Jewelry's inability

00:29:17.740 --> 00:29:18.940
to run the project

00:29:19.020 --> 00:29:20.220
due to a broken capital chain.

00:29:20.740 --> 00:29:21.860
Mr. Song, what do you think?

00:29:25.620 --> 00:29:26.220
Mr. Song.

00:29:27.700 --> 00:29:29.300
There's a document here
requiring your signature.

00:29:31.260 --> 00:29:32.020
I'll get back to work then.

00:29:38.460 --> 00:29:39.060
Mr. Song,

00:29:40.260 --> 00:29:41.700
I also suggest you

00:29:41.860 --> 00:29:43.460
gradually transfer the core team
to the new company.

00:29:44.580 --> 00:29:46.180
Ye Taiting wants Starlight Jewelry,
doesn't he?

00:29:47.100 --> 00:29:48.340
Let's just give him the empty shell.

00:29:51.740 --> 00:29:52.300
Baijian,

00:29:52.900 --> 00:29:54.140
your father

00:29:54.420 --> 00:29:55.980
has always valued
relationships and loyalty.

00:29:56.780 --> 00:29:59.860
I appreciate the thoughtfulness
from you and your father.

00:30:01.940 --> 00:30:03.260
But Zhizhi must have told you

00:30:03.780 --> 00:30:06.020
about my concerns.

00:30:11.740 --> 00:30:13.060
Mr. Song, I understand.

00:30:14.060 --> 00:30:16.020
You built Starlight Jewelry

00:30:16.140 --> 00:30:16.860
with painstaking effort.

00:30:17.300 --> 00:30:18.780
You've always treated it
like your own child.

00:30:19.660 --> 00:30:21.100
Giving it up would be like

00:30:21.460 --> 00:30:22.500
losing a part of yourself.

00:30:24.340 --> 00:30:25.140
And I guess

00:30:25.300 --> 00:30:27.100
you've also considered the shares
for the new company.

00:30:27.900 --> 00:30:28.900
The Ji family's involvement

00:30:29.180 --> 00:30:30.540
would inevitably dilute
the Song family's control.

00:30:31.740 --> 00:30:33.300
You're worried
about ending up with nothing.

00:30:38.420 --> 00:30:39.420
Don't worry about that.

00:30:40.220 --> 00:30:41.700
I've formally proposed to Zhizhi.

00:30:43.220 --> 00:30:44.420
And she has said yes.

00:30:44.780 --> 00:30:46.180
After we are married,

00:30:46.860 --> 00:30:48.900
the company will be registered
under both our names.

00:30:49.460 --> 00:30:50.980
It'll be our marital property.

00:30:51.700 --> 00:30:52.540
This new company

00:30:52.820 --> 00:30:54.300
will be entirely
under Zhizhi's management.

00:30:54.820 --> 00:30:55.700
She is more talented than I am

00:30:55.780 --> 00:30:56.940
in jewelry design.

00:30:58.660 --> 00:30:59.540
I'll fully support her

00:31:00.140 --> 00:31:01.300
and be her strongest backup.

00:31:04.420 --> 00:31:05.180
Baijian,

00:31:06.220 --> 00:31:08.780
since you're being so sincere,

00:31:09.780 --> 00:31:12.740
we'll go ahead with your plan.

00:31:14.380 --> 00:31:15.420
I trust your character,

00:31:16.100 --> 00:31:18.820
and I trust Zhizhi's choice.

00:31:21.540 --> 00:31:24.540
Then I'm entrusting my precious girl

00:31:25.380 --> 00:31:26.380
to you.

00:31:27.620 --> 00:31:28.700
You must treat her well.

00:31:29.260 --> 00:31:30.220
Don't let her down.

00:31:31.740 --> 00:31:34.340
You should move forward
with the wedding plans

00:31:34.700 --> 00:31:36.980
and the establishment
of the new company.

00:31:38.700 --> 00:31:39.660
Dad, don't worry.

00:31:40.020 --> 00:31:42.220
Baijian and I won't let you down.

00:31:55.580 --> 00:31:56.780
Found it!

00:32:02.060 --> 00:32:02.580
Zhizhi,

00:32:03.100 --> 00:32:05.420
look at you, always so rushed
and careless.

00:32:07.020 --> 00:32:08.700
I need to give you
a few words of advice.

00:32:08.700 --> 00:32:09.980
You're about to get married.

00:32:10.580 --> 00:32:12.980
You need to stop acting so spoiled.

00:32:13.500 --> 00:32:14.060
Dad,

00:32:14.660 --> 00:32:15.620
what are you talking about?

00:32:15.860 --> 00:32:17.180
I'm not that willful.

00:32:17.460 --> 00:32:18.140
You've got me wrong.

00:32:18.540 --> 00:32:19.260
I know

00:32:19.260 --> 00:32:20.380
my own daughter very well.

00:32:22.220 --> 00:32:23.180
Dad, look.

00:32:24.060 --> 00:32:25.700
I remember this photo

00:32:26.020 --> 00:32:28.180
was from when we went on
that trip together,

00:32:28.540 --> 00:32:30.220
and Zhiyan fell into the fountain.

00:32:31.700 --> 00:32:32.260
Yes.

00:32:32.700 --> 00:32:34.420
In the blink of an eye,
you've all grown so big.

00:32:36.820 --> 00:32:37.380
This one.

00:32:37.980 --> 00:32:41.140
This must be
from my fifth birthday, right?

00:32:45.300 --> 00:32:46.180
Is this Baijian?

00:32:47.140 --> 00:32:47.660
No.

00:32:48.220 --> 00:32:50.620
This is Ye Shengheng, the son

00:32:51.020 --> 00:32:51.740
of Ye Taiting's big brother.

00:32:53.500 --> 00:32:55.260
Such a pity. There was a car accident.

00:32:55.780 --> 00:32:56.620
And his whole family was gone.

00:32:58.900 --> 00:33:00.020
Baijian?

00:33:00.500 --> 00:33:01.620
He didn't come that day.

00:33:02.020 --> 00:33:03.100
I think he was sick.

00:33:03.500 --> 00:33:04.420
I specifically had someone

00:33:04.540 --> 00:33:05.540
deliver the gift to him.

00:33:08.780 --> 00:33:10.460
But when Baijian proposed,

00:33:10.460 --> 00:33:11.580
he said our first meeting

00:33:11.820 --> 00:33:13.380
was at my fifth birthday party.

00:33:14.260 --> 00:33:15.140
Could it be...?

